OL,3,CBT confirms loss of Belfast
OL,4,Cheadquarter jobs
OL,6,FTelecoms giant BT has confirmed it is
OL,7,Fto cut 90 customer service jobs at its
OL,8,FBelfast headquarters.
OL,10,FIt was annouced on Tuesday the
OL,11,FRiverside Tower office in Belfast will
OL,12,Fsee 90 people affected due to a
OL,13,Frestructuring of the
OL,14,Ftelecommunications company.
OL,16,FThe telecoms workers union, CWU said
OL,17,FBT had advised them of their need to
OL,18,Freduce costs in order to support the
OL,19,Ffunding of tools that will work to
OL,20,Fincrease their long-term business
OL,21,Fshare.
