OL,3,CBT confirms loss of Belfast
OL,4,Cheadquarter jobs
OL,6,FA BT Group spokesperson said: "Today,
OL,7,Fwe shared proposals with a small
OL,8,Fnumber of colleagues in Belfast to
OL,9,Ftransfer some of the work they do to
OL,10,Fother BT office locations.
OL,12,F"We are (in) discussions with anyone
OL,13,Faffected by our proposals and, if we
OL,14,Fgo ahead, we have shared other
OL,15,Fopportunities in the wider Belfast
OL,16,Foffice. There is no impact to
OL,17,Fcustomers.
