OL,3,CBT confirms loss of Belfast
OL,4,Cheadquarter jobs
OL,6,F"In 2023, we completed the multi-
OL,7,Fmillion-pound refurbishment of our
OL,8,Fflagship Riverside Tower office in
OL,9,FBelfast and we continue to invest in
OL,10,Fthe region."
OL,12,FBelfast remains a strategic location
OL,13,Ffor BT Group and is home to around
OL,14,F2,000 colleagues from across the
OL,15,Fcompany, including EE, BT Business and
OL,16,FOpenreach."
OL,18,FIn consultation with CWU, BT said the
OL,19,Fproposals were to close the customer
OL,20,Fservice provision operations in
OL,21,FBelfast.
